codex
The verifier itself is syntactically simple, but local `forge build` is crashing inside Foundry while trying to auto-install solc `0.8.19` for the archived `onchain_auto` sources. I’m checking whether I can isolate compilation to just `FlawVerifier.sol`; otherwise I’ll return the fixed source with that toolchain limitation called out.
